---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import TimelineComponent from "../../components/Timeline.astro";
---

<Layout title="Timeline">
	<div class="container">
		<section class="section">
			<p>The Timeline component displays chronological events in a visually appealing vertical layout. Perfect for showing project milestones, company history, process steps, or any time-based information.</p>
			
			<h2>Demo</h2>
			<div class="component-demo">
				<TimelineComponent
					title="Project Development Timeline"
					milestones={[
						{
							header: "Project Initiation",
							subHeader: "January 2024",
							details: [
								"Project kickoff and initial planning phase",
								"Team formation and requirements gathering",
								"Stakeholder meetings and goal setting"
							],
							active: true
						},
						{
							header: "Design Phase",
							subHeader: "March 2024",
							details: [
								"UI/UX design creation and wireframing",
								"User experience optimization",
								"Design system development"
							]
						},
						{
							header: "Development Sprint",
							subHeader: "June 2024",
							details: [
								"Core development phase implementation",
								"Feature development and testing cycles",
								"Code review and quality assurance"
							]
						},
						{
							header: "Beta Release",
							subHeader: "September 2024",
							details: [
								"Beta version launch with limited users",
								"User testing and feedback collection",
								"Bug fixes and performance optimization"
							]
						},
						{
							header: "Public Launch",
							subHeader: "December 2024",
							details: [
								"Official public release preparation",
								"Full feature set deployment",
								"Documentation and user guides"
							]
						}
					]}
				/>
			</div>

			<h3>Features</h3>
			<ul>
				<li>Clean vertical timeline layout</li>
				<li>Responsive design for all screen sizes</li>
				<li>Customizable event data structure</li>
				<li>Smooth animations and transitions</li>
				<li>Semantic HTML structure</li>
				<li>Accessible markup</li>
			</ul>

			<h3>Usage Example</h3>
			<pre><code>&lt;TimelineComponent
  title="Your Timeline Title"
  milestones={[
    {
      header: "Milestone Title",
      subHeader: "Date or Phase",
      details: [
        "Detail point 1",
        "Detail point 2"
      ],
      active: true
    }
  ]}
/&gt;</code></pre>

			<h3>Milestone Data Structure</h3>
			<p>Each milestone in the timeline should have the following structure:</p>
			<ul>
				<li><strong>header</strong>: Main title for the milestone</li>
				<li><strong>subHeader</strong>: Date or phase information</li>
				<li><strong>details</strong>: Array of detail points for the milestone</li>
				<li><strong>active</strong>: Optional boolean to highlight the current milestone</li>
			</ul>

			<h3>Use Cases</h3>
			<ul>
				<li>Project milestones and roadmaps</li>
				<li>Company history and achievements</li>
				<li>Process workflows and steps</li>
				<li>Event chronologies</li>
				<li>Product development timelines</li>
			</ul>
		</section>
	</div>
</Layout>